      "content": "that's a good start. can u go deeper with the logic though? like, help me explain why the \"meritocracy\" argument people usually make is kind of a flawed or even unfair way to look at it? i want to show that the idea that anyone can just \"work hard and succeed\" doesn't really apply when there's so much systemic stuff in the way.",
